<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.9">
<l>kuṭikuṭi yākak kūṭiniṉ ṟamarar kuṇaṅkaḷē pitaṟṟiniṉ ṟētta</l>
<l>vaṭiyavark karuḷi yaravaṇait tuyiṉṟa vāḻiyā ṉamarntuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>kaṭiyuṭaik kamala maṭiyiṭai malarak karumpoṭu peruñcenne lacaiya</l>
<l>vaṭivuṭai yaṉṉam peṭaiyoṭuñ cērum vayalveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells, resting, the one with the discus</l>
<l rend="indent">who sleeps on the serpent couch, blessing his devotees,</l>
<l>While immortals, continually gathering as families, praise [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">continually babbling [his] qualities,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Veḷḷiyaṅkuṭi with paddy fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where shapely swans join with their mates,</l>
<l>As sugarcane and enlarged red paddy sway, while fragrant lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">bloom at [their] feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
